Package: zvplot
Title: Theme and utilites for ggplots (and other graphics) in a personal style
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Zak",
      family = "Varty",
      email = "z.varty@imperial.ac.uk",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Functions and colour defintions to help create and export ggplot2 plots in the style that is 
    consistent with that of zakvarty.com. The two primary functions style and export ggplot plots.
